{
  "stem": "13874.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After our mother died, our uncle, who lived with us and ran our business continued to live with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even wherever we were, whether it was Wurzburg, or whether it was Munich, our home was Lehrberg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we always came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we kept the housekeeper after our mother's death, and she rents the house for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was general.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing too overt or nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was accepted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most countries, and Germany in particular, there was always latent anti-Semitism, just like in the United States and every place else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You just learned to live with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took it for granted, just the way I took for granted that my father was dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's part of-- it was part of life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it-- it was around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That-- my-- we just were different, which-- which was accepted, and no fuss was made about it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, there's one thing which people don't realize.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were Germans and felt like Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] All our [INAUDIBLE], and including my father, were in World War I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother had two brothers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We considered ourselves Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was very patriotic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even after he was wounded in World War I, he volunteered to go back to the front.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was his Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My uncle, too, he was part of being [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a veteran of the German wars.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On my father's side, he had two brothers, one who died in Romania, and the other one who was wounded and later who had a head shot.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
